005package edu.wpi.first.hal.simulation;
006
007import edu.wpi.first.hal.JNIWrapper;
008
009/** JNI for analog output data. */
010public class AnalogOutDataJNI extends JNIWrapper {
011  public static native int registerVoltageCallback(
012      int index, NotifyCallback callback, boolean initialNotify);
013
014  public static native void cancelVoltageCallback(int index, int uid);
015
016  public static native double getVoltage(int index);
017
018  public static native void setVoltage(int index, double voltage);
019
020  public static native int registerInitializedCallback(
021      int index, NotifyCallback callback, boolean initialNotify);
022
023  public static native void cancelInitializedCallback(int index, int uid);
024
025  public static native boolean getInitialized(int index);
026
027  public static native void setInitialized(int index, boolean initialized);
028
029  public static native void resetData(int index);
030
031  /** Utility class. */
032  private AnalogOutDataJNI() {}
033}
